# -*- mode: org -*-

* build
  make server-init
  NOTE: catch, websocketpp and json are header libraries and cloned
  from github. opencv2 has to be compiled another place for the
  moment. it is necessary to copy core/ core.hpp and libopencv
  _core.so.3.1.0 to the opencv2 directory created in lib/ (notenote: this is done by the makefile)

  make server-build

* start
  make start
